The Jackdaw pirates have captured Demmi Beetlestone, and written the Ministry Guard to demand a ransom. As the Legate Minister's daughter, Demmi could bring quite a price. Too bad the Order of Whispers is involved—and planning to spring her well before her father's soldiers can arrive.
